structure.unit: Jurisdiction And Emblems Of The Commonwealth, The General Court, Statutes And Public Documents

law.catch_line: Journals Of Senate And House Of Representatives; Copies
law.text: [ Text of section added by 2012, 165, Sec. 5 effective January 1, 2013. See 2012, 165, Sec. 137.] Such number of copies of the journals of the senate and of the house of representatives as the committees on rules shall determine shall be printed annually under the direction of the clerks of the 2 branches.
